# CODEOWNERS - Define code ownership for automatic review requests
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything in the repo
# These owners will be requested for review when someone opens a PR
*                       @org/maintainers

# Documentation
/docs/                  @org/tech-writers
*.md                    @org/tech-writers
README.md               @org/maintainers @org/tech-writers

# Source code by area
/src/api/               @org/backend-team
/src/frontend/          @org/frontend-team
/src/shared/            @org/backend-team @org/frontend-team

# Infrastructure and DevOps
/.github/               @org/devops
/infrastructure/        @org/devops
/docker/                @org/devops
Dockerfile*             @org/devops
docker-compose*.yml     @org/devops

# Configuration files
*.config.js             @org/maintainers
*.config.ts             @org/maintainers
/config/                @org/maintainers

# Security-sensitive files
/config/prod*           @org/devops @security-lead
SECURITY.md             @security-lead
.github/workflows/      @org/devops @security-lead

# Dependencies
package.json            @org/maintainers
package-lock.json       @org/maintainers
requirements.txt        @org/maintainers
pyproject.toml          @org/maintainers

# Database
/migrations/            @org/backend-team @dba-team
/schema/                @org/backend-team @dba-team

# Tests
/tests/                 @org/qa-team
/__tests__/             @org/qa-team
*.test.js               @org/qa-team
*.spec.ts               @org/qa-team

# Specific critical files
/src/auth/              @security-lead @org/backend-team
/src/payments/          @org/backend-team @finance-lead
